m someone named Azmodane claiming to be a GM. The asked if I knew anything about Show EQ or Linux. I said I had heard of them but had never used them. They asked a number of questions and claimed my account had been flagged but that it might have been their problem and an error. That perhaps no &quot;warning&quot; or banning of account was needed.  They then asked for my login and password claiming they needed to check history and that I did not even have to log off for them to do it.  I did not reply and did a who all and the person was anon and certainly not identified as a GM or Guide.  They repeated the request for password and log in stressing I did not have to log off, a which point I replied that until they had a GM next to their name they could kiss my ass.<br>
  With a least a minor amount of humor they replied *kisses ass*.<br>
 Of course I filed a /report and a petition on it. <br>
 Of course I have heard no more about it from the GMs.<br>
<br>
 Be advised and beware.<br>
